      <h1 style="font-size:2rem;line-height:1.35;">CBAM默认排放因子的非对称效应：高效生产商为何承担了不相称的碳成本</h1>
      <div class="article-meta">
        <span>2026-05-20</span>
        {tags.filter(Boolean).map(t => <span class="tag">{t}</span>)}
